<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3>Welcome to Rohan Academy, <%= @user.name %>! </h3>
    <p>
      You could <a href="<%= new_user_session_url %>"> sign in to Rohan Academy</a> with the credentials:
    </p>
    <p>
      Username: <strong><%= @user.name %></strong><br>
      Email: <strong><%= @user.email %></strong><br>
      Password: <strong><%= @user.cl_password %></strong><br>
    </p>
    <p>
      You could also use these email, password to login to <a href="https://convertlabs.io"> ConvertLabs</a> site.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>